---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { analyticsEvents, heatScoreWeights, recommendedFunnels } from '../data/analyticsPlan';
---

<BaseLayout title="运营埋点与内容热度方案 - ai-productivity" description="ai-productivity 的前端事件、内容热度计算和运营漏斗规划，用于后续接入 GA、Cloudflare Analytics 或数据库。" canonical="/analytics-plan/" robots="noindex,follow">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-sky-700">Operations</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-slate-950 sm:text-5xl">运营埋点与内容热度方案</h1>
    <p class="mt-5 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">这个页面用于内部运营规划，汇总当前站点已经触发的前端事件、建议关注的漏斗，以及后续内容热度计算方式。页面设置为 noindex。</p>

    <section class="mt-12 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950">当前事件清单</h2>
      <div class="mt-6 overflow-x-auto">
        <table class="w-full min-w-[760px] border-collapse text-left text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 text-slate-700">
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">事件名</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">分类</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">用途</th>
              <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">关键参数</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            {analyticsEvents.map((event) => (
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-100 align-top">
                <td class="px-4 py-4 font-mono text-xs font-semibold text-sky-700">{event.name}</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-4 text-slate-700">{event.category}</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-4 leading-6 text-slate-600">{event.purpose}</td>
                <td class="px-4 py-4 text-slate-600">{event.keyParams.join(', ')}</td>
              </tr>
            ))}
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-10 grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950">内容热度分数</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">后续接入数据库或分析 API 后，可以按下面权重生成热门内容榜，用于首页排序、内容更新优先级和专题推荐。</p>
        <div class="mt-5 space-y-3">
          {heatScoreWeights.map((item) => (
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
              <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
                <div class="font-semibold text-slate-950">{item.label}</div>
                <div class:list={['rounded-full px-3 py-1 text-sm font-bold', item.weight > 0 ? 'bg-emerald-50 text-emerald-700' : 'bg-rose-50 text-rose-700']}>{item.weight > 0 ? `+${item.weight}` : item.weight}</div>
              </div>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">{item.reason}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950">推荐观察漏斗</h2>
        <div class="mt-5 space-y-5">
          {recommendedFunnels.map((funnel) => (
            <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-950">{funnel.name}</h3>
              <ol class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
                {funnel.steps.map((step, index) => (
                  <li class="flex gap-3">
                    <span class="flex h-6 w-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white text-xs font-bold text-sky-700">{index + 1}</span>
                    <span>{step}</span>
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ol>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-10 rounded-3xl border border-sky-100 bg-sky-50/70 p-6 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-950">下一步接入建议</h2>
      <ol class="mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">
        <li>1. 在 GA4 中创建与上述事件同名的自定义事件。</li>
        <li>2. 将 <code>prompt_copy</code>、<code>feedback_mailto_submit</code>、<code>submit_prompt_mailto</code> 标记为关键事件。</li>
        <li>3. 如果需要精确内容热度，后续用 Supabase 或 Cloudflare D1 保存事件副本。</li>
        <li>4. 每周导出热门内容、催更内容和低反馈内容，驱动内容更新计划。</li>
      </ol>
    </section>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
